prompt.title: Embedding for When to Use Promptbook
prompt.content: Promptbook is recommended for use when writing apps that generate complex content via LLM, separating code from text prompts, describing complex prompt pipelines, orchestrating multiple prompts, and versioning prompts. It's not recommended for simple, single-prompt implementations or when OpenAI Assistant (GPTs) is sufficient.
